OL,3,CWales appoints new Chief Medical
OL,4,COfficer
OL,6,FProfessor Isabel Oliver has been
OL,7,Fappointed as the new Chief Medical
OL,8,FOfficer for Wales.
OL,10,FShe'll replace Sir Dr Frank Atherton
OL,11,Fwho stands down at the end of the
OL,12,Fmonth after eight and a half years in
OL,13,Fthe role.
OL,15,FHe told ITV Wales' political programme
OL,16,FSharp End this week that the Covid-19
OL,17,Fpandemic was a highlight, saying "I
OL,18,Fdon't think we made any fundamental
OL,19,Fmistakes, the lockdown processes saved
OL,20,Flives.
