OL,6,F"We need to learn and look back to see
OL,7,Fif there's any tweaks we could make to
OL,8,Ffuture pandemic management."
OL,10,FAs Chief Medical Officer for Wales,
OL,11,FProfessor Oliver will provide clinical
OL,12,Fleadership and be responsible for
OL,13,Fproviding independent professional
OL,14,Fadvice to the Welsh Government about
OL,15,Fhealth and public health matters.
