OL,3,CWales appoints new Chief Medical
OL,4,COfficer
OL,6,FShe will also work with organisations
OL,7,Facross Wales to reduce health
OL,8,Finequalities and lead the medical
OL,9,Fprofession with the aim of improving
OL,10,Fthe quality of healthcare and patient
OL,11,Foutcomes.
OL,13,FProfessor Oliver will be joining the
OL,14,FWelsh Government from her role as
OL,15,FDirector General of Science and
OL,16,FResearch and Chief Scientific Officer
OL,17,Fat the UK Health Security Agency
OL,18,F(UKHSA).
