OL,3,CWales appoints new Chief Medical
OL,4,COfficer
OL,6,FShe said "It is an honour to be
OL,7,Fappointed as the Chief Medical Officer
OL,8,Ffor Wales and I am very excited to
OL,9,Fwork with the dedicated health
OL,10,Fprofessionals and the communities
OL,11,Facross Wales to create a Healthier
OL,12,FWales and safeguard our NHS.
OL,14,F"Today, we face challenges from our
OL,15,Fageing population, inequalities and
OL,16,Fglobal factors such as climate change.
