OL,3,CWales appoints new Chief Medical
OL,4,COfficer
OL,6,F"For someone like me with a great
OL,7,Fpassion for health and wellbeing,
OL,8,Fthere are some unique opportunities in
OL,9,FWales to secure major improvements in
OL,10,Fpublic health and health services for
OL,11,Fall, thanks to innovative policies and
OL,12,Feffective collaboration between
OL,13,Fsectors and it will be my privilege to
OL,14,Fserve the people of Wales to secure
OL,15,Fhealthy, resilient and prosperous
OL,16,Fcommunities."
