OL,3,CWales appoints new Chief Medical
OL,4,COfficer
OL,6,FCabinet Secretary for Health and
OL,7,FSocial Care, Jeremy Miles, said
OL,8,F"Professor Oliver brings a wealth of
OL,9,Fexperience to Wales after working at a
OL,10,Fsenior level in public health in the
OL,11,FUK and I look forward to working with
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,F"I'm delighted she has joined us as we
OL,15,Fwork to improve health and wellbeing,
OL,16,Fand I'd like to offer her a warm
OL,17,Fwelcome to Wales."
